program to print fibonocci series

n = int(input("Enter the nth term: "))
a = 0
b = 1
sum = 0
count = 1
print("Fibonacci Series: ")
while(count <= n):
  print(sum)
  count += 1
  a = b
  b = sum
  sum = a + b
else:
    print("Invalid")
